review:
Beautiful game [b]BUT YOU MUST HAVE  VERY VERY STRONG NERVES.[/b]

[u]Typical play[/u]: the first level (of a set) is simple enough. Any other level is about a quarter of an hour, with several nervous breakdowns, numerous rages quit, and [i]in fine[/i] use cheat code.

The main problem that will it you on the head is the camera. It frequently chooses not to look where you want, and even follow the liquid drop (after it splits) that you don't want.

If I should rank this game :
[list]
[*] Graphics / Animations:  5 / 5;
[*] Platform: 5 / 5 [i](works great on Linux)[/i];
[*] Gameplay [i](user inputs)[/i]:  1 / 5;
[*] Camera:  1 / 5;
[/list]
